OL,3,CMother who contracted Covid tells
OL,4,Cinquiry she had to wear PPE as baby
OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FA bereaved mother has told the UK
OL,8,FCovid-19 Inquiry that she had to wear
OL,9,Ffull PPE as her baby son died in her
OL,10,Farms hours after he was born during
OL,11,Fthe pandemic.
OL,13,FCatherine Todd said she did not feel
OL,14,Fsafe in hospital in Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fafter contracting Covid while pregnant.
OL,17,FModule three of the inquiry, chaired
OL,18,Fby Baroness Heather Hallett, is
OL,19,Finvestigating the impact of the
OL,20,Fpandemic on healthcare systems across
OL,21,Fthe UK.
