OL,7,FIt heard evidence on Wednesday morning
OL,8,Ffrom Ms Todd, a member of the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Covid Bereaved Families for
OL,10,FJustice group.
OL,12,FHer newborn son Ziggy died in the
OL,13,FUlster Hospital on July 21 2021.
OL,15,FThe inquiry was told that Ms Todd was
OL,16,Fapproaching 28 weeks pregnant when she
OL,17,Fcontracted Covid during that month.
OL,19,FShe said this led to the cancellation
OL,20,Fof a routine pregnancy scan.
