OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FMs Todd said she later began to feel
OL,8,Funwell and was concerned that her
OL,9,Funborn baby was not moving.
OL,11,FShe said she called the hospital
OL,12,Fmaternity unit several times and was
OL,13,Ftold to take paracetamol, lie on her
OL,14,Fside and take a fizzy drink.
OL,16,FShe told the inquiry: "They told me
OL,17,Fthey wouldn't bring me in at the time
OL,18,Fbecause they wanted to reduce the risk
OL,19,Fof spread of Covid."
