OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FMs Todd said she believed she would
OL,8,Fhave been seen earlier if she did not
OL,9,Fhave Covid.
OL,11,FAfter her condition worsened, she
OL,12,Fphoned her GP who told her to attend
OL,13,Fthe hospital's accident and emergency
OL,14,Fdepartment.
OL,16,FShe told the inquiry that after
OL,17,Fwaiting in A&E for 10 hours, she was
OL,18,Fmoved to the maternity section and an
OL,19,Femergency section was carried out amid
OL,20,Fconcerns about a lack of amniotic
OL,21,Ffluid around the baby.
