OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FShe said her partner TJ was not
OL,8,Fallowed to visit her at this time.
OL,10,FWhen her son Ziggy was born he was
OL,11,Ftaken to the neonatal intensive care
OL,12,Funit and placed in an incubator
OL,13,Fovernight, the inquiry was told.
OL,15,FCounsel to the inquiry Nick Scott
OL,16,Fasked: "Do you think the fact that you
OL,17,Fwere Covid-positive had anything to do
OL,18,Fwith the amount of information you
OL,19,Fwere given about Ziggy's condition
OL,20,Fovernight?"
