OL,5,Cdied
OL,7,FShe said: "Yes, I think they were
OL,8,Ftrying not to come in and out of the
OL,9,Froom as much as they would have if I
OL,10,Fwasn't Covid-positive."
OL,12,FMs Todd said she and her partner were
OL,13,Fbrought to see Ziggy the following
OL,14,Fmorning, believing that his condition
OL,15,Fwas improving.
OL,17,FShe said: "They took everything off
OL,18,Fand handed Ziggy over to me and then
OL,19,Fthey just left the room and then he
OL,20,Fpassed away and they didn't come back
OL,21,Ffor about two hours."
