OL,7,FMr Scott said: "Was that the first
OL,8,Ftime you had been with Ziggy since he
OL,9,Fwas born?"
OL,11,FShe replied: "Yes."
OL,13,FHe added: "Were you having to wear
OL,14,Ffull PPE when you were with him?"
OL,16,FShe said: "Yes. We had hairnets,
OL,17,Fmasks, a visor, gloves and shoe
OL,18,Fcoverings.
