OL,7,F"I thought that was unnecessary. At
OL,8,Fthe time they knew how unwell he was.
OL,9,FI am a bit confused why we were in
OL,10,Ffull PPE."
OL,12,FAsked about the impact of having to
OL,13,Fwear the protective gear, Ms Todd
OL,14,Fsaid: "All of our photos we have with
OL,15,Fhim are in full PPE."
OL,17,FFollowing Ziggy's death, his body was
OL,18,Ftaken to a hospital in Liverpool for a
OL,19,Fpost-mortem examination.
