OL,7,FMs Todd told the inquiry that for two
OL,8,Fdays before Ziggy's body arrived at
OL,9,FAlder Hey Hospital, she did not know
OL,10,Fwhere his remains were.
OL,12,FMr Scott asked: "When you look back on
OL,13,Fall of your experiences in July 2021,
OL,14,Fdo you think there were enough staff
OL,15,Fto treat you at that time?"
OL,17,FShe said: "No."
OL,19,FHe said: "Do you think the staff knew
OL,20,Fhow to treat a pregnant woman with
OL,21,FCovid back in 2021?
